Description:
You arrive at some kind of party. It seems that the cultists are organizing a banquet for the new members. They seem too drunk or immersed in the party to be bothered by your presence here.

This is the perfect place to use the scroll that Belphyor gave you.

You notice that some cultists are playing a drinking game. Maybe you can talk to them or join the game to extract useful information.
